item.title: About
item.author: dave@davenull.us (David Bird)
item.description: Hello, I am David Bird. I am a JavaScript hacker, Linux abuser, and lover of all things FOSS. I am the lead developer/engineer for the Soapbox Alert System, and creator of the Slater School Bell Platform.
